modules.description: This module manipulates OCaml abstract syntax trees by attaching documentation, metadata, and configuration options to labels and types, primarily supporting command-line interface generation. It operates on Ppxlib AST types like `label_declaration`, `type_declaration`, and `expression`, transforming them into structured expressions and code artifacts. Its functionality is particularly useful for automating the derivation of CLI parsers from type definitions in OCaml projects leveraging the Cmdliner library.
